  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cheria</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>.........</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル、どうかしたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel, what's wrong?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>過去に戻って歴史を変える事が
正しいとは決して思わない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't think going back to the past to
change history is ever the right thing to do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だが俺には、彼らの気持ちもわかるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I do understand how they feel.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺も昔、かけがえのないものを
失ってしまったから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I lost something irreplaceable in the past, too...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからもう二度と失わない為に
俺はすべてを守ってみせると誓ったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why I swore to protect everything I could.
To never lose anyone like that again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もちろん、シェリアの事も守るさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And to protect you, too, of course.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう。　気持ちは嬉しいわ。
だけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you. I'm happy to hear that.
But...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
